Package: shapeconnect
Title: Calculate Fragment Connectivity Index 
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Felix", "May", email = "felix.may@posteo.de", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package calculates a fragment-level connectivity index
  based on a raster map. The connectivity index considers the distances
  among fragments, as well as their shapes and areas.
Depends: R (>= 3.4.2)
